title: Watch: Softball Player Decimates Dodgeball Opponents
text:
Screengrab via prestonfrsh/YouTube BTW 
Sans any context—which is fine because it would be utterly superfluous—comes the video, "When You play dodgeball with a Softball player." 
What do you think happens? 
Did you guess ridiculous head snipes and brutal chest shots? 
That's just what happens.
